nodes.text: The Invasion of Kashyyyk was a conflict in the Galactic Civil War that took place in 4 ABY. During the invasion, which followed the initial invasion in 19 BBY, the Galactic Empire was allied with Trandoshan slavers, and together they enslaved much of the Wookiee population. The Imperials were commanded by Moff Darcc and the slavers by Pekt. The invasion was followed by the liberating of the planet by New Republic forces.
